nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 20
Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 20 is the twentieth issue of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine. It was released on September 24, 2013.
It contained the comics Seeds (reprinted from Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.49) and Deadly Allies (reprinted from Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.51).
